OL,3,CMan killed in synagogue attack
OL,4,C'stabbed multiple times' by terrorist
OL,6,FA father-of-three died from multiple
OL,7,Fstab wounds inflicted by terrorist
OL,8,FJihad Al-Shamie during the attack on a
OL,9,FManchester synagogue, a coroner's
OL,10,Fcourt has been told.
OL,12,FMelvin Cravitz, 66, died along with
OL,13,FAdrian Daulby, 53, when Al-Shamie
OL,14,Ftargeted the Heaton Park Hebrew
OL,15,FSynagogue in Crumpsall, on 2 October.
OL,16,FThree others were injured in the
OL,17,Fattack.
