OL,6,FManchester Coroner's Court also heard
OL,7,Fhow Mr Daulby, known as the "quiet
OL,8,Fhero" who barracked the synagogue
OL,9,Fdoors, died from a single gunshot
OL,10,Fwound to the chest, fired by an armed
OL,11,Fpolice officer.
OL,13,FMoments earlier, Mr Cravitz was killed
OL,14,Fafter being stabbed by the terrorist
OL,15,Fwho began his attack by driving his
OL,16,FKia Picanto at security staff and the
OL,17,Fexternal gates of the synagogue around
OL,18,F9:30am.
