OL,6,FThe hearings, in front of Her Honour
OL,7,FJudge Alexia Durran, the Chief Coroner
OL,8,Fof England and Wales, were brief and
OL,9,Fwere adjourned ahead of full inquest
OL,10,Fhearings on 18 February 2026.
OL,12,FAl-Shamie rang 999 during his deadly
OL,13,Frampage, pledging allegiance to the so-
OL,14,Fcalled Islamic State terror group,
OL,15,Fbefore he was shot by armed police.
