OL,3,CMan killed in synagogue attack
OL,4,C'stabbed multiple times' by terrorist
OL,6,FHe drove his car at Jews gathering for
OL,7,Fthe holy day of Yom Kippur then
OL,8,Fattacked others with a knife and tried
OL,9,Fto storm the synagogue, wearing a fake
OL,10,Fsuicide belt, before being shot dead
OL,11,Fby armed police.
OL,13,FChief Supt Lewis Hughes of Greater
OL,14,FManchester Police (GMP) told the
OL,15,Fhearing on Wednesday, 29 October, that
OL,16,FAl-Shamie had used his car, then got
OL,17,Fout to attack worshippers.
