OL,6,FHe said: "The offender exited the
OL,7,Fvehicle armed with a knife and
OL,8,Fimmediately made stabbing motions to
OL,9,FMr Cravitz's upper torso, head and
OL,10,Fneck area."
OL,12,FMembers of the public and the
OL,13,FCommunity Security Trust (CST) gave
OL,14,Ffirst aid and CPR and the victim was
OL,15,Ftaken to the Manchester Royal
OL,16,FInfirmary where he was pronounced dead
OL,17,Fat 10.45am.
